{"tid":1421602,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"放棄呢場運動吧啦！","createTime":"2019-08-06T08:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T09:12:11.000Z","uid":53639,"like":2,"dislike":176,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"b069c4a84387cf503c78b9843e689ab42dfaf643","tid":1421602,"uid":53639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"日日都聽到咁多深藍嘅說話<br />\n聽到有種無力感，好攰、好抑鬱<br />\n<br />\n班深藍每次都淨係識話班後生有破壞無建設<br />\n係踐踏緊上一代嘅貢獻、建設<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地話我地呢場運動先係真正破壞經濟、令呢個社會受損嘅主謀<br />\n倒不如就如佢地所講，放棄呢場運動，等佢地同佢地嘅承受返個惡果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知實會俾人罵我軟弱，但我更加唔想呢一班辛苦為未來努力嘅每一位一次又一次俾人咒罵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位辛苦晒！<br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢時見到好多真正香港人，互相幫助嘅場面真係好感動"},{"pid":"a87ef4be1aa8166275d1fa64237b8c2f6d6fcdd0","tid":1421602,"uid":12628,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:29:37.000Z","msg":"你走啦，交比其他人得喇"},{"pid":"9a23f145f90a26d972c2dc1a62fbb30b7d9964b6","tid":1421602,"uid":174289,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"要放棄自己放 咪撚拉人走 垃圾散水撚！"},{"pid":"c8d7c0572705311896ab8a1f682931761a3a761f","tid":1421602,"uid":48358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"你咪放棄 無人想知"},{"pid":"ef745fa4861250ad86e23465761ca0a974591242","tid":1421602,"uid":86118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"躝啦你"},{"pid":"6a63661c184f767b35fc336460cbb1bd2ea36827","tid":1421602,"uid":79571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:30:24.000Z","msg":"你想放棄就自己走"},{"pid":"396602c7d10119a54b040ac9b458f080b5ca227a","tid":1421602,"uid":281918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:30:46.000Z","msg":"放你老母"},{"pid":"e11818cb1a55d0f4a4b38eb44530c4d0d4f4ff8d","tid":1421602,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:08.000Z","msg":"如果你唔係三毛 你一定係個弱智"},{"pid":"ea1c3db0f6bda874cac9e4ee5b10e8a896ebd85c","tid":1421602,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:25.000Z","msg":"放你老母！<br />\n咁撚多位手足為咗呢場運動可能要坐10年，<br />\n對得住佢地？"},{"pid":"9a9e0cdca687a86c468a605dd8e1a9f70c8d67b9","tid":1421602,"uid":281960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"On9  永不放棄"},{"pid":"47e964d38233544968f13c94da803de4473ce831","tid":1421602,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"咪on9,到佢地受個陣起碼有1半老死左啦<br />\n試下聽日收佢層樓 激過妳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df78d478713410e3f117a572e6694adfdb841e5","tid":1421602,"uid":253833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:32:42.000Z","msg":"散水撚<br />\n和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76c3e9166d0e1a89dbaba9e4a354bdac1529efdc","tid":1421602,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"我都好攰，但諗起犧牲自己前途啲手足，呢啲算係咩！你如果係男人，見到前線啲絲打仲講唔講得出呢啲說話，慚唔慚愧？"},{"pid":"d591d03c5df330d0a70d900f70fb2751f8900567","tid":1421602,"uid":177851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇人想知你諗咩啊</span>"},{"pid":"53db6c33dc948d996a977949aa49f0bfda90543f","tid":1421602,"uid":107950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"放棄就乜都冇，努力咗咁耐為乜"},{"pid":"fef79a83dd1e717f0497ad7bc7349a7302bac75a","tid":1421602,"uid":298949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"自己想退就退, 唔使同人交代 <br />\n場仗未打完架<br />\n散水撚可恥"},{"pid":"ba768375fec70d692b1224007320fb7c8fda05fa","tid":1421602,"uid":30503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:37:54.000Z","msg":"點對得住被捕人士，，你係咪政府人員"},{"pid":"21437bd50e63cb8d0cd992ae